Subject: [PATCH] imx8-mipi-csi2-sam.c: Add debug = 1

Add debug = 1 to print summary of communication errors

Signed-off-by: Erik Schumacher <erik.schumacher@iris-sensing.com>
Signed-off-by: Jasper Orschulko <jasper@fancydomain.eu>
---
 drivers/staging/media/imx/imx8-mipi-csi2-sam.c | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/staging/media/imx/imx8-mipi-csi2-sam.c b/drivers/staging/media/imx/imx8-mipi-csi2-sam.c
index cfd60bb755a6..0f57a49f90ac 100644
--- a/drivers/staging/media/imx/imx8-mipi-csi2-sam.c
+++ b/drivers/staging/media/imx/imx8-mipi-csi2-sam.c
@@ -447,7 +447,7 @@ struct csi_state {
 	u32 val;
 };
 
-static int debug;
+static int debug = 1;
 module_param(debug, int, 0644);
 MODULE_PARM_DESC(debug, "Debug level (0-2)");
 
